by w w w . H i p 4 H o p . r o - C A R E E R F R O M P A S S I O N !

This course will create a foundation for every bboy where he will be able to develop his own style.

First Chapter is the Groove .In this chapter you will learn way you must mantain and develop the groove on all levels

The Second Chapter is the Levels . Here you will learn the concept where you subcategorize breaking on levels not toprock or footwork or anything else.

The Third Capter is Symmetry on Levels.You will learn to play with the levels in a symmetryc way
title: Online Bboy Technique - Learn to dance in a symmetric way !
